-- China Plans Measures to Coax Private Investments in Urban Sewage
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2013-10-16T10:39:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-16/china-plans-measures-to-coax-private-investments-in-urban-sewage.html
China plans to implement measures to
attract private investments in the construction and operation of
urban drainage and sewage infrastructures, according to a State
Council statement on the central government’s website.  It also said without elaborating that the world’s most
populous nation is planning to further strengthen the management
of drainage and urban sewage treatment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Hackley in London at 
